App sends POST to /login
request body is
username=daddy&password=daddy123			// where daddy is username of user,daddy123 is password

---------------------------------

controller returns:
{
"result":"n1",
"userid":"id",
"username":"daddy",
"name":"tanmay tiwari",
"email":"emseg@gsgjle.com",
"privacy":"3"		//see privacy documentations
}

where
n1=
0:ok logged in
1:no such user or wrong password
2:already logged in(maybe from some other account), so ask user to log out first
7:error

id=
userid of user 			(store it locally)